statements: SELECT id, page_url, time_visited, user_id, user_behavior, performance_metrics FROM WebsiteAnalytics;
SELECT page_url, user_id, time_visited FROM WebsiteAnalytics WHERE user_id = 123;
SELECT * FROM WebsiteAnalytics ORDER BY time_visited DESC;
SELECT AVG(user_id) AS avg_user_id, COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM WebsiteAnalytics WHERE user_id IS NOT NULL;
SELECT page_url, COUNT(*) AS page_visits FROM WebsiteAnalytics GROUP BY page_url ORDER BY page_visits DESC;
SELECT id, page_url, time_visited, user_id, user_behavior, performance_metrics FROM WebsiteAnalytics WHERE user_id = 123 ORDER BY time_visited DESC
SELECT * FROM WebsiteAnalytics WHERE page_url LIKE '%homepage%' ORDER BY id ASC
SELECT user_id, COUNT(*) AS page_views FROM WebsiteAnalytics GROUP BY user_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 5 ORDER BY page_views DESC
SELECT id, page_url FROM WebsiteAnalytics WHERE JSON_EXTRACT(performance_metrics, '$.load_time') > 1000
SELECT * FROM WebsiteAnalytics WHERE user_behavior LIKE '%clicked%'
SELECT * FROM website_traffic;
SELECT page_url, timestamp FROM website_traffic WHERE id = '123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000';
SELECT id, page_url, ip_address FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, action FROM user_behavior WHERE device_type = 'mobile' AND timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT MAX(timestamp) AS latest_timestamp FROM user_behavior;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE page_url LIKE 'example%' ORDER BY timestamp DESC;
SELECT id, page_url FROM website_traffic WHERE timestamp > '2022-01-01' AND ip_address = '192.168.1.1';
SELECT page_url, COUNT(*) AS visit_count FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_url HAVING visit_count > 10 ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT u.user_id, COUNT(*) AS action_count FROM user_behavior AS u INNER JOIN website_traffic AS w ON u.user_id = w.id GROUP BY u.user_id HAVING action_count > 5;

SELECT w.page_url, u.action, w.timestamp FROM website_traffic AS w INNER JOIN user_behavior AS u ON w.id = u.user_id WHERE w.timestamp >= '2022-01-01' AND u.device_type = 'mobile' ORDER BY w.timestamp ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_date > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, page_name FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_date DESC;
SELECT * FROM user_behavior WHERE action = 'click';
SELECT id, metric_name, metric_value FROM performance_metrics WHERE metric_value > 100.00;
SELECT id, action, timestamp FROM user_behavior ORDER BY timestamp;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31' ORDER BY page_name DESC;
SELECT page_name, COUNT(page_name) AS page_visits FROM website_traffic GROUP BY page_name ORDER BY page_visits DESC;

SELECT page_name, SUM(metric_value) AS total_metric_value FROM website_traffic JOIN performance_metrics ON website_traffic.id = performance_metrics.id GROUP BY page_name ORDER BY total_metric_value DESC;
SELECT user_id, action, COUNT(action) AS action_count FROM user_behavior WHERE timestamp >= '2022-01-01' GROUP BY user_id, action ORDER BY action_count DESC;

SELECT page_name, AVG(metric_value) AS average_metric_value FROM website_traffic JOIN performance_metrics ON website_traffic.id = performance_metrics.id GROUP BY page_name HAVING AVG(metric_value) > 100 ORDER BY average_metric_value ASC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic;
SELECT id, page_url FROM website_traffic WHERE page_url LIKE '%about%';
SELECT id, visit_timestamp FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC;
SELECT user_id, action, action_timestamp FROM user_behavior WHERE action = 'click' AND user_id = 101;
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM performance_metrics WHERE metric_value > 0.5 ORDER BY metric_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_timestamp DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, page_url FROM website_traffic WHERE page_url LIKE '%blog%' ORDER BY id ASC;
SELECT AVG(metric_value) AS average_metric_value, MAX(metric_value) AS max_metric_value FROM performance_metrics;
SELECT user_id, action, action_timestamp FROM user_behavior WHERE action = 'click' AND action_timestamp > '2022-01-01';
SELECT id, log_timestamp, UPPER(log_message) AS uppercase_message FROM optimization_logs WHERE log_message LIKE '%error%' ORDER BY log_timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
SELECT * FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_date DESC, visit_time ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_url, visit_date FROM website_traffic WHERE visit_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY page_url;
SELECT user_id, action, timestamp FROM user_behavior WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM performance_metrics WHERE metric_value > 100 ORDER BY metric_value DESC;
SELECT username, email FROM user_profiles ORDER BY username ASC;
SELECT * FROM user_profiles WHERE username = 'john_doe';
SELECT order_id, total_amount, user_id FROM user_orders WHERE total_amount > 1000 ORDER BY order_date DESC;
SELECT user_id, action, page_viewed FROM user_behavior WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-01';
SELECT metric_name, metric_value FROM performance_metrics WHERE metric_value < 0.5 ORDER BY metric_value DESC;
SELECT id, page_url, visit_date, visit_time FROM website_traffic ORDER BY visit_date, visit_time ASC;
